github/workflows/release.yml (L104 to 116)
  Note: The workflow verifies the signature locally, then exports the public key and publishes it as a mutable release asset alongside the zip and signature.

issues/038-about-official-distribution-and-pgp.md (L18 to 20)
  Note: The acceptance criteria explicitly avoid showing the release signing fingerprint in the information screen, removing an important out-of-band trust anchor.
```
